鐘意邊個迪士尼樂園嘅機動遊戲同卡通人物，佢講講吓話試過之前去，戴住頂有米奇老鼠耳仔嘅帽，又同廿幾人一齊行，但係冇人發現係佢。同埋佢話而家鐘意去環球片場多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有fans問可唔可以睇吓佢同Kenji一齊唱歌，佢話佢開緊演唱會，早幾日又去FNS，再之前喺邊個縣開演唱會都唔記得。有時喺屋企都係佢老公做家務，佢攰到攤喺梳化度冇哂力咁講「唔該&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n同埋例牌講吓佢啲人生觀，又提到出道前去啲bar度唱，畀人話佢唱得難聽。之後又發生失言事件，所以曾經有段時間過得好辛苦。不過佢相信第二日會有新轉變，結果捱過咗，今日先可以嚟到兵庫縣唱歌畀大家聽。所以佢短期內都唔會引退，大家可以放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEjm98Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEjm98Q.jpg&h=bde7c58b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDQEWOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDQEWOR.jpg&h=0ee72fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcPeLG7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcPeLG7.jpg&h=8c67be8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hvJD18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hvJD18.jpg&h=9e62b995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSSDsVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSSDsVp.jpg&h=5e67ea68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNuN5G3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNuN5G3.jpg&h=013b4b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhojcm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzhojcm1.jpg&h=0f306393&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3ec6b3ef8b41970a1ef6bd5203331755ede10a3","tid":930624,"uid":102336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"仲有佢話今年第一次12月31號開countdown live，不過好多人上佢啲社交網站度寫抽唔到，所以決定會直播，話喺我哋呢場度首先公布，17:00先正式喺網站公布，不過應該好多人都睇咗<br />\n<br />\n同埋就係6、7號係ayu喺呢個場開，8、9號就係佢開。佢話ayu啲dancer喺後台留咗言畀佢啲dancer，佢放咗上Instagram<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bb7957